              We believe every frame tells a story. Our mission is to provide world-class photography and videography services.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div className="space-y-4">
            <h4 className="text-accent font-serif font-bold">Contact</h4>
            <p className="text-gray-400 text-sm">hello@luminaframes.com</p>
            <p className="text-gray-400 text-sm">+1 (555) 000-FRAMES</p>
          </div>
        </div>
